        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/7/1",
        "text": [
          " قَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ حَكَمَ فِي دِرْهَمَيْنِ فَأَخْطَأَ كَفَرَ \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3229 - It is narrated from Abu Basir that Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"Whoever judges in a matter of two dirhams and errs has disbelieved.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
