        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/7/2",
        "text": [
          " : \"أَيُّ قَاضٍ قَضَى بَيْنَ اِثْنَيْنِ فَأَخْطَأَ سَقَطَ أَبْعَدَ مِنَ اَلسَّمَاءِ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3230 - Muawiyah ibn Wahb narrated from Abu Abdillah (as) that he said:\n\"Any judge who judges between two people and errs falls farther than the distance between the heavens.\""
          ]
        }
      }
